duck: Hooke's law - In mechanics and physics, Hooke's law of elasticity is an approximation that states that the extension of a spring is in direct proportion with the load applied to it.
English physicist, inventor, and mathematician who formulated the theory of planetary movement.
Hooke (lunar crater) - Hooke is a lunar crater that is located to the northwest of the crater Messala, in the northeastern part of the Moon.
